videos.headline: Virginia's Reed opens game with kickoff return TD
videos.description: Virginia WR Joe Reed takes the kickoff and bursts up the field for a 98-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Navy answers back with Abey TD
videos.description: Navy's Zach Abey takes the QB keeper and scores the 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Perry's TD run gives Navy lead
videos.description: The Midshipmen's Malcolm Perry runs the read option and keeps it himself for the 22-yard touchdown to give Navy a 14-7 against Virginia.

videos.headline: Williams makes impressive pick  for Navy
videos.description: Virginia QB Kurt Benkert throws a desperation deep ball on 3rd down and CB Sean Williams makes a leaping grab for the interception.

videos.headline: Navy's Perry rips off nice run for big gain
videos.description: Malcolm Perry finds a gap in the defense and races up the field for a 33-yard scamper.

videos.headline: Perry's 2nd TD extends Navy lead
videos.description: Midshipmen's Malcolm Perry bursts through the defense behind great blocking and takes it in for a 19-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia committs costly turnover
videos.description: Cavaliers' RB Joe Reed fumbles the exchange from Kurt Benkert and Tyler Sayles recovers for Navy.

videos.headline: Navy's ground game can't be stopped
videos.description: Zach Abey runs the option and easily scores a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Navy's Perry leaves game with injury
videos.description: Malcolm Perry is spun around on the tackle and injures  right foot.

videos.headline: Abey's 3rd TD gives Navy commanding lead
videos.description: Zach Abey runs the read option and follows his blockers into the end zone for the 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Abey runs in his fourth TD for Navy
videos.description: Zach Abey calls his own number and speeds up the left side of the field for a 20-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Abey is a workhorse on 5th TD
videos.description: Zach Abey spins into the endzone for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Navy's Abey wins Military Bowl MVP
videos.description: QB Zach Abey had a huge day, rushing for 88 yards and 5 touchdowns to lead Navy to a 49-7 victory over Virginia.
